OWASP
-	Open Web World Wide Application Security Project 
-	OWASP top 10 – helps web application security testers understand the web application security issues and how to remediate them. 
-	Open OWASP Zap, select the first option, and start the machine scan. Select the first option on your left, Zap automated scan
Just so you know, OWASP Zap is very intrusive, so please make sure you have permission before running it on any system. 
Why is a web vulnerability scan important? Because it is defensive reconnaissance—finding your weaknesses before attackers do.

OWASP Zap found vulnerabilities with colored flags indicating the level of severity. 

